United States: repetition is the mother of wisdom
It is comical that Barack Obama, the president with the reputation of wise, reproduced the strategy of his predecessor on the Afghan question, which he considered himself as simple.
When he finally revealed his Afghan approach, eagerly awaited, it showed that it is a copy of the script used to Iraq by Bush three years ago.
Not content to use in the text several times the expression " as in Iraq ", he has not hesitate to use the title of Bush's statement in January 2007 as the name of his own speech: " a new way forward "
Has he himself three years ago, the personally criticized the idea of Bush to send new military reinforcements to Iraq, by the civil war as " irresponsible and in their conclusions karastrophische decision ".
The following month, however, showed that the Bush strategy, based on the recommendations of the only possible and captains of countryside, was do not speak today in the news about Iraq.
Bush's reputation has not improved, however objectively speaking, it was left to his successor a final situation much more favourable than expected.
In Afghanistan, Barack Obama hopes to repeat the miracle.
In order to increase the contingent have asked the military It again, especially the commander of the Afghan operation General Stanley McCristal, even despite the trench in the White House.
He called for 40,000 men in order to improve the situation.
The president has hesitated for three months, but in the absence of a better option, at least misled the general about 10,000 soldiers.
From Europe, has the promise for a further 5,000, even though He himself.
The most problems throughout the strategy Obama seems to be his intention to withdraw troops from Afghanistan in 18 months and finish this process within three years. The whole doctrine of Obama raises more questions than answers.
Many doubt that the increase in the same fruit that the procedure in Iraq.
Despite the fratricidal wars in recent years, the society of Iraq is relatively well organised, their leaders to respect the agreements.
The Afghan situation is characterised by the exact opposite - we cannot rely on anyone and no treaty is respected.
Under these conditions, it is difficult to prepare the Afghan security forces, if they are used to change every day.
The political institutions, although formally established, will remain just a people proliferate the patriarchal ethnic relations.
Balancing the interests of various ethnic groups is unusually complicated, particularly because of the even more complicated by the Pakistani and Iranian influences.
Even the building of a " strong state ', which is the minimalist objective of the whole operation, does not seem to be very real.
The time horizon of the Obama strategy by his voluntarism
Over the past eight years, the situation in Afghanistan has worsened and now it is on the fringes of chaos.
Only a romantic soul, to believe that the small soldiers in the war and reality can be sent to " soon return home " will bring a miracle.
From a political point of view, set a date for the withdrawal of troops is purely irresponsibility, because the Taliban will see this as the indirect admission of the American defeat.
The last NATO summit showed that the willingness of the Europeans to participate in military operations in Afghanistan.
European politicians do not know or do not want to explain to their constituents, what has the security of Germany or Italy with the war with the Hindu Kush.
Another possible factor that can influence the situation radically, is the development of events in Iran.
If the situation continues to deteriorate and sanctions have no effect on the Iranians, the Americans will have to make a difficult decision: try to solve the problem with military force or not.
It will respond by example when, according to Obama, America will come to the winner withdrawal of troops from Afghanistan.
Any solution will also mean a dramatic turn of the Afghan situation.
The only positive point for Barack Obama is the fact that there are three years until the presidential election and therefore there is still enough time to working on a new strategy, if it is a total failure.
The managers of the bank Goldman Sachs will receive no bonuses in cash
Senior executives of the US bank Goldman Sachs will receive no bonuses this year more in cash.
The company announced that it has responded to the sharp criticism of its pay practices.
The group of 30 senior managers will receive shares instead of money, they will not sell within five years.
In addition, The actions can be withdrawn in the event that they would take too risky.
According to Reuters, Goldman Sachs thus became the leader in the effort to link the bonuses with long - term performance on Wall Street.
I suppose that Wall Street is well aware of the overall sense that we must take, said the former investment banker of society's, Douglas Elliott.
The problem is in the details, he added.
The bank Goldman Sachs became the target of criticism after being set aside almost $17 billion in premiums for the first three quarters of this year.
For this year, the total amount of premiums will probably exceed $20 billion despite the measure announced today, according to Reuters.
The high bonuses in the banking sector became, With the arrival of the financial crisis, in a sensitive political issue in many countries.
Britain announced Wednesday that it plans to tax at once, with a tax of 50 per cent, the bonuses exceeding 25,000 pounds.
France is also preparing similar measures.
This year, women received the Nobel Prizes in all categories less physical
Five women, which is a record, received today in Stockholm in the hands of the King of Sweden this year's Nobel prizes in the technical categories and for literature.
In addition to the four scientists there was also the German writer of Romanian origin Herta Müller.
The Nobel Prize for Medicine have Two American biologists, Elizabeth Blackburn and Carol Greider, together with her compatriot Jack Szostak for research in the field of chromosomes.
The prize for chemistry was awarded to the Israeli Ada Jonath with the Americans Venkatraman Ramakrishnan and Thomas Steitz for clarification of the structure and function of the ribosomas.
The last winner received the Nobel Prize for economics, the American Elinor Ostrom and his compatriot Oliver Williamson for their analysis of the economic report.
The only specialist category, without a woman, was physics.
This prize was presented today scientists Charles Kao for his research in the field of optical fibres and George Smith with Willard Boyle for the invention of the chip, which are the basis of all digital cameras, fax or telescope.
Each winner received the diploma, the Nobel medal and certificate of the money received.
It reached 10 million Swedish kronor in each category. (approximately 1.1 million euros) .
If one of them has several winners, they will share the reward them.
The much - anticipated Nobel Peace Prize has this afternoon in Oslo, Norway, US President Barack Obama.
In his speech, acknowledged the controversial nature of his as it is at the beginning of his career and is also at the head of a country engaged in two wars in Iraq and Afghanistan.
In the discharge of its policy he added that in certain situations the war is essential to achieve peace, even if the price is high.
