According to the new schedule of the ČD there will be fewer trains for the same charges.
The Czech rail or limited from 13 December some less its Schnell - and local trains, other links will be strengthened.
The total length of transport volume will be reduced from the day of entry into force of the new schedules of two percent compared to today.
Most of the charges including the basic price and customer will not change.
These for example, the inhabitants of the to the capital of the work area, the railway sets for this type pendolino trains.
The direct train, On the contrary, will not be Bratislava.
There will also be less fast trains on the line Prague - Písek - České Budějovice, the direct links Prague - Letohrad.
In the regions, the largest reduction in transportation is in the region of Hradec Králové eight percent in total, to an increase in Prague and environment.
Two night trains on the Prague - Tábor - České Budějovice are also cancelled and some fast trains in the line Prague - Písek - České Budějovice is reduced to just a few days of the week.
One of the biggest changes is the introduction of a new hotline of Milovice to Prague, the inhabitants of Milovice must change in Lysá nad Labem.
It is the fifteenth line of the commuter system Esko, whose opening is possible thanks to the completion of the electrification of the line of Lysá nad Labem and Milovice.
The links long distances to the capital will end up in the station Prague Hlavní nádraží.
The ČD will introduce more lines SC Pendolino between Prague and Ostrava and trains to Šumperk/Jeseník move every two hours.
Travellers can no longer take the Pendolino to Bratislava from 13 December.
The bill this year for the regional rail: 200 million
The fast trains are ordered and paid by the Ministry of Transport, to cover the so - called the railways next year in all four billion kronor the same amount as this year. Local trains are ordered by the regions, next year will pay eight billion kroner in total, and the state will help them almost three billion.
This year the regional trains are 200 million more expensive.
For The railways have newly signed a contract for ten years, until now the Treaty was always a year.
The railway praises the system, it is not to the increase in the price of the vast majority of tickets.
The changes will affect only tickets a day ČD net and Internet tickets at reduced prices eLiška.
For passengers without the customer card will increase the price of ČD net of 450 kroner to 600 kronor.
The price of eLiška will depend on the distance, until now there was a single price of 160 kroner for travel between any two regional cities.
The rebels still hold more than 50 people, The children were released
The rebels have kidnapped today 75 people in the southern Philippines, including some primary school pupils and their teachers.
The agency AFP, which originally only about 65 Entführte informed.
All 17 children held were released after eight hours, including a teacher.
The abduction occurred in the province of Agusan del Sur.
It is reported that about 19 rebels have used the hostages as human shields during a flight to the police.
The local negotiators are trying to find an agreement for the publication of the remaining hostages.
According to the AFP agency, the rebels belong to the New People's Army (NPA) , which is the armed wing of the Communist Party of the Philippines (CPP) .
According to the AFP agency the police initially pursued the kidnappers because of the violence, which was the cause a settling of accounts between two family clans.
In the south of the Philippines in the province of Maguindanao, was because of the recent massacre, in which 57 people died, imposed Martial law.
Among the victims of the massacre of 23 November, related to the election to the administration of the Governor, 30 journalists.
The suspicion of involvement in the massacre arrested the governor of the province in the southern Philippines and his father Andal Ampatuan, patriarch of the influential Ampatuan.
On The island of Mindanao also includes Muslim separatists.
However on Tuesday renewed peace talks with the Philippine government.
The history of South Africa affects everyone, says Morgan Freeman alias Mandela
In The next few days, the new Hollywood film Clint Eastwood arrives in US cinemas Invictus (his official title in Czech esinvictus: Neporažený) , and narrae part of the biography of the former President of the Republic of South African Nelson Mandela.
The role of the world - famous fighter against apartheid is Morgan Freeman, who chose years ago by Mandela himself to embody.
The second male role of the legendary champion South African rugby has been attributed to Matt Damon.
With the arrival of the film in cinemas, the critics and the public are heard.
Nelson Mandela
Its full name is Nelson Rolihlahla Mandela, born on 18 July 1918 in South Africa.
In 1988 he was awarded the Sakharov Prize for freedom of spirit, in 1993, alongside de Klerk, the Nobel Peace Prize.
He was President of the Republic of South Africa from 1994 to 1999.
Great expectations are placed in The film, because he comes at a time when the South Africa is in full preparations for the World Cup, and secondly At the same time the media by alarming news about the growing racial hatred and discrimination of the people on the part of the black majority.
According to the news agency AP are the responses to the new film in South Africa for the time being consistently positive, despite many reservations about the distribution of the main roles where " pavanent " Hollywood stars.
Morgan Freeman is nevertheless, using his own words, proud of the film.
I dreamt of this role for many years and I am well prepared.
