The World championship heavyweights
Hot in Bern: Kevin Johnson the challenger constantly verbally and gestuellement the world champion Vitaly Klitschko with words and gestures.
But after twelve rounds difficult Ukrainian defended his title of heavyweight in the version of the WBC.
The verdict of the judges was unanimously.
Hamburg - Vitaly Klitschko remains world heavyweight champion.
The champion of 38 years in the version of the partnership WBC defeated in the night of Saturday in Bern the American Kevin Johnson by unanimous decision by points (120: 10) .
For Klitschko it was the third successful defence of the title since his return in October 2008.
Previously, the Ukrainian was already twice world champion of associations WBO and WBC.
Unfortunately, it was not possible to make the noqueo that everyone had hoped for.
Klitschko his record to 39 victories in 41 professional fights, twice had to be overcome because of injuries.
The challenger Johnson had to accept the first defeat in his fight number 24.
About 17,000 spectators In the Berne arena wanted to dictate the 2.02 metres wide Klitschko the fight with his left hand.
But Johnson, 11 centimetres smaller, before the duel had proclaimed the end of the era Klitschko, was again and again the blows of the world champion, so that Klitschko could not crucial to the goal.
Overall, the passive Johnson did too little for a challenger, and tried to move the rounds.
Although he provoked Klitschko with words and gestures, its blows only rarely reached the world champion.
Still, he is now the second boxer after Timo Hoffman in the year 2000, have exceeded with Klitschko distance of twelve rounds.
The challenger had done a lot of noise in the Swiss capital before the fight.
He offended Klitschko as " ugly zombie ", the " can do nothing right ".
The weight, the champion was left on Friday to Johnson the sun glasses of the nose " in order to be able to see his eyes. "
Fourth victory since the comeback of Klitschko.
Klitschko remained in his fourth fight after his return on 11 October 2008, invincible.
After a break of almost four years, he had beaten at the time the Nigerian Samuel Peter in Berlin and recovered " his " of the WBC belt, which he had previously had to surrender without a fight.
This year, defending his title of champion, he won the battle against Juan Carlos Gomez of Cuba and in September against Chris Arreola, of the United States.
I only have a stroke in this fight, and I am in perfect form, " said Klitschko to explain his rapid return to the ring.
His dream remains, But the unification of all four major titles in his family.
His brother Vladimir is world champion of associations WBO and IBF.
However, the belt belongs to the British David Haye, after this in November the 2.13 meter Nikolai Walujew.
In the summer, Haye had cancelled a fight against Vitali Klitschko planned for September.
Supposedly is planning its promotion society now the fight against Klitschko in London's Wembley Stadium.
The case Kunduz
Frontal attack from the opposition: the head of the Group of the Greens, Jürgen Trittin, accused the Minister of Defence Guttenberg of lying in the case of false information on the case Kunduz.
The SPD and the Left demand explanation to the Chancellor.
Hamburg/Berlin - following the most recent revelations about the air attack in Kunduz, the opposition has criticized the Defence Minister Karl - Theodor zu Guttenberg (CSU) , have cheated with knowledge of the facts.
The Minister said the deadly bombing of two on Saturday, transmitted by The television channel ARD, the head of the Group of the Greens, Jürgen Trittin, said in the news programme ".
This means that he lied.
The order to kill, was in breach of the rules of the International Security Assistance Force in Afghanistan (ISAF) .
This is the substance of the report that had NATO, and that has been read by Mr Gutenberg, said Trittin.
On Friday, it was revealed that the attack was not just a destruction of the kidnapped vices, but also to kill two Taliban leaders.
In the air attack According to investigation report of NATO, 142 people had been killed or injured was launched at the request of Colonel Klein, commander of Kunduz.
The Greens, the SPD and the Left on Saturday called for Chancellor Angela Merkel (CDU) , to decide as soon as possible before the federal Parliament and to clarify what really knew about the incident.
Mrs Merkel must clarify whether a strategy of intentional killing is part of the federal government's Afghanistan policy - and whether chancellor, German army and intelligence service have approved this new strategy, Jürgen Trittin the colleague from the Greens Renate Künast.
The government spokesman Ulrich Wilhelm rejected the criticism.
The chancellery not exerted any influence on concrete actions of the German army in Afghanistan, he said.
