75% of working mothers have had problems because of their maternity
The Discrimination in the work has increased in recent years, especially for women in the younger generation who want to be mothers.
It reveals the study " fertility and career women in Spain, " conducted by the CSIC in collaboration with the Institute of women.
The survey of 9,737 women aged between 15 to 75 years leaves no doubt about it: 75% of working mothers saw their career opportunities in the workplace because of motherhood.
The study indicates that there are many differences in the beginning of life as a couple and the number of children, depending on whether or not the women work and the type of work.
Those who do not work outside the home, working part - time work or have a stable work not have their first pregnancy earlier and have more children.
By contrast, women with a stable employment, mainly in the public sector, the creation of a family and motherhood, and therefore have fewer children.
Women between 35 and 49 years with a fixed work have their first child, on average, 3.7 years after being installed as a couple. This figure that rises to 4.1 women with have needed more time in your life to achieve them, which has led them to postpone the union and the arrival of children.
In addition, the type of work played exerts great influence on motherhood, albeit less on the timing of the pairing, " explains the researcher of the CSIC Margarita Delgado.
The level of education is another factor that widens the gap of the age of marriage for women and their first child.
According to the survey, the higher the level of training, the more they marry and have their first child.
The difference is also among women of the same generation.
For example, in the group between 35 and 49 years, those who have elementary and higher education have been mothers for the first time to 25.1 and 32.1 years on average.
" another is also among women, depending on their level of education.
While those who have studies elementary marry and have their first child before finding a stable job, those of average levels or higher invest this sequence and give priority to obtaining a stable work as a prerequisite to marriage and the arrival of a child, " Delgado.
