Cowardly aggression
Last week, my mother, who was about 70 years of age by our neighbourhood in the municipality of Fuenlabrada, when a group of young people between 15 and 18 years, to her and our dog, a sang - mélé, rescued the perrera and with no more than six kilos, and without saying a word, they beat him two kicked that left the dog seriously injured.
Our outrage is great because we do not find the fun in a gratuitous attack to a small and defenceless animal, which of course, was leash.
Add to this the indignation of a woman who was walking quietly and that, when these individuals came to fear for their physical integrity, attacking an animal is capable of doing the same thing to a woman, a child, an elderly man or, weaker than him.
The incident occurred at 5 p. m. on a Tuesday as another in a normally quiet.
The dog was crying all day.
