At the wheel of the Porsche Boxster Spyder
For the development of their latest and very expensive jewel used the engineers Boxster S as a base and that adelgazase nothing less than 80 kilos, which has left the báscula in only 1,275 kilograms.
This has led to happen, first, the automatic roof has been replaced by a roof manual, save 21 kilos; using doors of aluminum as the GT3, ' other 15 kilos of the climatizador, 13; reducing the fuel tank from 64 to 54 litres, 7 kilograms of 12 and with the slight of 19 inches, five.
Finally, they have renounced the audio system Cdr - 30 brought six kilograms and changing the doors for each question, the remaining kilo.
Although the model also exists with the Doppelkupplungsgetriebe PDK available, the test was carried out on a unit with the manual box of six speeds, mainly for secondary roads of California, in the mountains, with particularly tortuous.
His behaviour can only be described as beyond reproach.
The weight does not prevent the car to drive on the ground with aplomb.
Rather, the contrary: it was a long time that we had not tested a model so small and light that, at the same time, including at high speed.
It is a small athlete, able to heat their muscles in a short running for as long as necessary, until we ask him to sprinter, to recover and grow again its engine ...
It is out what we wanted. Through his leadership, as communicative as precise, the car will do what our hands on the steering wheel.
And it will do so with surgical precision.
His engine at will
The sound of his V6 boxer, with 320 horsepower (10 more than the Boxster S) is particularly successful and can be strengthened with the option " sport " or through a system that changes the roar of the engine, already used on the Panamera.
The ability of acceleration is brutal, whether from unemployed or in recoveries.
The suspensions are strong, but not hard or inconvenient.
The asphalt roads that we have travelled with the Boxster Spyder was quite damaged, but the car meisterte the potholes.
The electronic assistants had barely act of presence throughout the journey; and that in some of the curves ice at dawn and gravel, later in the morning.
In summary, a car, more fun to drive and that is much more than a simple amendment of the Boxster S.
The car will be on sale in February 2010, at a price of 70.831 euros.
